    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it's honestly been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape, looks great, and has been well-cared for since I got it. It drives like a dream and is perfect for anyone looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today! I\u2019m super excited for its next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you\u2019d like to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system for optimized volumetric efficiency across the RPM range. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve shim adjustment and a thorough inspection of the rear subframe mounting points for structural integrity. The suspension maintains its factory-spec kinematics, providing the telepathic steering feedback these chassis are known for. A well-sorted example for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain health and performance dynamics.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Clean title. Maintenance up to date. Interior and exterior well-kept. Runs well.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a wonderful example of pride in ownership, offering a reliable and polished driving experience. The exterior paint holds a beautiful shine, complemented by the original alloy wheels which are free of major curbing. While there are a few minor cosmetic blemishes\u2014specifically some light peppering from road debris on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger door\u2014the body is straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the cabin feels fresh and inviting. The leather seats are in great shape with only minor softening on the driver's entry point, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats throughout its life. All interior electronics, including the infotainment screen, heated seats, and navigation, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts through all gears with precision. It has been serviced according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a multi-point inspection already completed. This car is ready for the road and needs nothing but a new driver.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
